BM <value>        ; set B-field setpoint (engineering units, e.g., amperes)
BR <rate>         ; set ramp slew rate (units per second), positive number
BS START          ; begin ramping toward current BM target
BS STOP           ; stop ramp (hold current DAC)
BF <freq> <amp>   ; enable LF modulation (Hz, peak amplitude in same units as BM)
BF OFF            ; disable LF modulation
BO 0/1            ; output enable (1) / disable (0) to the DAC for magnet
Q?                ; query: returns a status line (see below)
ESTOP             ; immediate output disable + zero setpoint
